        beamGroups: [[2, 8], [2, 8]],
        tip: "Standard \"spang-a-lang\" ride pattern, all notes on the <strong>bow</strong> of the ride — about a third of the way out from the bell. Listen to the steady <em>ping</em>. This is your reference timbre. Treat the swung 8ths as triplets with a rest in the middle."
