        tip: "China + snare alternating 8ths over <em>16th</em> kicks. This is the canonical extreme blast — the cymbal hand on the china (for sheer volume above the wall of guitars), and the kick foot doing twice the work of the hands. Don't try this until the previous three exercises are clean. The kick foot has to be louder than your fear."
