        tip: "Snare on <em>3</em> only — no snare on 2. Kick on 1 and 4. The metronome is still clicking at ♩=100, but the groove will feel like ♩=50. Don't rush to fill the space where the 2 used to be; the emptiness is the entire point of the half-time feel."
