        beamGroups: [[2, 8], [2, 8], [2, 8], [2, 8]],
        tip: "Snare on the <em>&amp; of 1</em> and the <em>&amp; of 4</em> — not on 2 and 4 at all. The bar has two snare hits but they're displaced from the expected positions. The listener's ear keeps trying to hear them as 2 and 4 and the music keeps refusing. Bruford built whole tracks around this kind of perceptual misalignment. Hold the displacement; do not resolve back to 2-and-4."
